  "detailed_description": "<strong>A Simple VR Arcade Style Rail Shooter </strong><br><br>Early Access - Fully Playable Levels<br><br>Enjoy taking turns with your friends with this twin gun shooter<br>A range of themed levels including; <br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Halloween Theme: Simple!! Just shoot all of the pumpkins!<br></li><li>Western Theme: Shoot all bottles, explosives and other objects to gain points and coins<br></li><li>Snow Theme: The snowmen have stolen of the gifts! Retake as many gifts as you can, destroy the snowmen before they take them back from you!  </li></ul><br>Still to come; <br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>More themed levels Pyramids, Mine-Carts, Sci-fi Drones? Broomsticks?<br></li><li>Easter Eggs!<br></li><li>Steam Achievements </li></ul><br>For best experience, put a chair in the middle of your play space and align chair to the game vehicle while in the menu screen.",
